A '''Global Communications Transponder''' (GCT) was an illegal device used for transponding communications.

[[Takara]] possessed one, and was able to hear [[Ka'Pa]]'s communications. Ka'Pa himself loathed it and ordered [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] to steal it from Takara in order to aid the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]].

